*everybuddy-0.4.3 (1 Aug 2002)

  22 Jan 2003; Martin Holzer <mholzer@gentoo.org> everybuddy-0.4.3.ebuild :
  added media-libs/audiofile to dependency cause of the -laudiofile flag.
  Closes #14376.

  05 Jan 2003; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> everybuddy-0.4.3.ebuild :

  NLS bloat reduction.

  01 Oct 2002; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org> :
  Made it link against libaudiofile 8488

  1 Aug 2002; Gabriele Giorgetti <stroke@gentoo.org> everybuddy-0.4.3.ebuild:
  New version, updated deps for esound and gnome-libs.

